      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "fef8b79678501fa5",
      "text": "WEINSTEIN, Alexander, 2017. “Oomph-Making Machines”: An Interview with [[George Saunders]]. Pleiades: Literature in Context. 2017. Vol. 37, no. 1, p. 66–70.  [https://doi.org/10.1353/plc.2017.0025 doi]"
